description:
&quot;Salt is a game based around exploration and adventure where you sail across a vast ocean exploring different islands. The world of Salt is procedurally generated, providing you with an endless amount of exploration. During your adventure you will meet various challenges and obstacles that you will have to overcome, as well as discovering the real story behind the world of Salt. You will fight pirates, hunt animals for food, defend yourself from enemies at night, sail the ocean waves, craft items from resources you find throughout the world, and discover mysterious places throughout your adventure.&quot;
More info at https://saltthegame.com/pages/saltoverview/

